\c 24
\p
\s Dhavhidhi anokamura vapirisiti
\p
\v 1 Zvino mapoka avanakomana vaAroni akanga akadai: vanakomana vaAroni: Nadhabhi, naAbhihu, naEriazari, naItamari.
\v 2 Asi Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa vasina vana, baba vavo vachiri vapenyu; saka Eriazari naItamari vakabata basa roupirisiti.
\v 3 Dhavhidhi, pamwechete naZadhoki, mumwe wavanakomana vaEriazari, naAhimereki, mumwe wavanakomana vaItamari, vakakamura sezvavakanga vagoverwa mabasa avo.
\v 4 Vakawana vakuru vazhinji pakati pavanakomana vaEriazari kupfuura pakati pavanakomana vaItamari; vakakamurwa kudai : Pakati pavanakomana vaEriazari kwakanga kuna vane gumi navatanhatu, vaiva vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba; napakati pavanakomana vaItamari, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo vakanga vari vasere.
\v 5 Nokudaro vakakamurwa nemijenya, mumwe pano mumwe koko; nokuti kwakanga kuna machinda eimba tsvene, namachinda aMwari pakati pavanakomana valtamari.
\p
\v 6 Shemaya mwanakomana waNetaneri, munyori, akanga ari wavaRevhi, akavanyora pamberi pamambo, namachinda, nomupirisiti Zadhoki, naAhimereki mwanakomana waAbhiyatari, navakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avapirisiti navaRevhi; vachitsaura mhuri imwe kuna Eriazari, nemhuri imwe kuna Itamari.
\p
\v 7 Zvino mujenya wokutanga wakabata Jehorayaribhi, wechipiri Jedheiya;
\p
\v 8 wechitatu Harimi, wechina Seorimi,
\p
\v 9 weshanu Marikiya, wetanhatu, Miyamini,
\v 10 wechinomwe Hakozi, worusere Abhija;
\v 11 wepfumbamwe Jeshua, wegumi Shekania;
\v 12 wegumi nomumwe Eriashibhi, wegumi nemiviri Jakimi;
\v 13 wegumi nemitatu Hupa, wegumi nemina Jeshebheabhi;
\v 14 wegumi nemishanu Bhiriga, wegumi nemitanhatu Imeri;
\v 15 wegumi neminomwe wegumi nemisere Hapizeri;
\v 16 wegumi nemipfumbamwe Petahia, wamakumi maviri Jehezekeri;
\v 17 wamakumi maviri nomumwe Jakini, wamakumi maviri nemiviri Gamuri;
\v 18 wamakumi maviri nemitatu Dheraya, wamakumi maviri nemina Maazia.
\p
\v 19 Ndiko kukamurwa kwavo pamabasa avo, kuti vapinde imba yaJehovha pavakanga varairwa napo naAroni baba vavo, sezvaakarairwa naJehovha Mwari walsiraeri.
\s Vakuru vavanakomana vaRevhi
\p
\v 20 Kana vari vamwe vanakomana vaRevhi, vanakomana vaAmirami: Shubhaeri; vavanakomana vaShubhaeri: Jedheiya.
\p
\v 21 VaRehabhia: vavanakomana vaRehabhia: Ishia mukuru.
\p
\v 22 Vavalzhari: Sheromoti; vavanakomana vaSheromoti: Jahati.
\p
\v 23 Vavanakomana vaHebhuroni: Jeria mukuru, naAmaria wechipiri, naJahazieri wechitatu, naJekemeami wechina.
\p
\v 24 Vanakomana vaUzieri: Mika; vavanakomana vaMika: Shamiri
\v 25 Munun'una waMika: Ishia; vavanakomana vaIshia Zekariya.
\v 26 Vanakomana vaMerari: Mari naMushi; vanakomana vaJazia: Bheno.
\v 27 Vanakomana vaMerari: vaJazia: Bheno, naShohami, naZakuri, naIbhiri.
\v 28 VaMari: Eriazari, wakanga asina vanakomana.
\v 29 VaKishi: vanakomana vaKishi: Jerameeri.
\v 30 Vanakomana vaMushi: Mari, naEdheri, naJerimoti. Ndivo vakanga vari vanakomana vaRevhi, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo.
\p
\v 31 Naivo vakakandawo mijenya sehama dzavo, ivo vanakomana vaAroni pamberi pamambo Dhavhidhi, naZadhoki, naAhimereki, navakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba dzavapirisiti navaRevhi; dzimba dzamadzibaba dzomukuru dzaiverengwa sedzomunun'una wake.
